<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 12:36:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>石油价格上涨冲击风险资产，比特币难以守住 70,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/bitcoin-dips-below-70-000-as-energy-prices-surge</link><description>由于中东能源基础设施再次遭受攻击，股市下跌，能源价格飙升，比特币一周多以来首次跌破 70,000 美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iachV4Bf6Dj4/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 08:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/bitcoin-dips-below-70-000-as-energy-prices-surge</guid></item><item><title>前妻离婚后被指控盗窃 1.8 亿英镑比特币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/ex-wife-accused-of-stealing-180-million-in-bitcoin-after-divorce</link><description>离婚后，一名丈夫指控前妻密谋窃取价值数百万美元的比特币和豪华手表，此案将考验英国民事法院如何对待数字资产。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVvrnnfg0iIU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/ex-wife-accused-of-stealing-180-million-in-bitcoin-after-divorce</guid></item><item><title>随着避险情绪上升，比特币三周来跌幅最大</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/bitcoin-retreats-from-six-week-high-as-iran-conflict-escalates</link><description>由于伊朗紧张局势升级引发全球市场广泛避险情绪，比特币创下三周以来最大跌幅。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ic.B_Ak0Wghs/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 14:18:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/bitcoin-retreats-from-six-week-high-as-iran-conflict-escalates</guid></item><item><title>人工智能、加密货币在伊利诺伊州初选中遭遇意外失败</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/ai-crypto-suffer-surprise-defeats-in-illinois-primary-fights</link><description>伊利诺伊州的民主党选民本周拒绝了加密货币和人工智能行业支持的大多数候选人，这标志着资金雄厚的特殊利益集团在准备花费数亿美元在今年的中期选举中塑造国会时意外失败。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.DGru0nGTno/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 15:05:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/ai-crypto-suffer-surprise-defeats-in-illinois-primary-fights</guid></item><item><title>美国和其他国家寻求影响力，敦促英国禁止加密货币捐赠</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/uk-urged-to-ban-crypto-donations-as-us-and-others-seek-influence</link><description>由于人们越来越担心包括美国在内的外国的影响，英国立法者正在推动政府立法禁止向政党捐赠加密货币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQGpBIg3B6wY/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 13:55:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/uk-urged-to-ban-crypto-donations-as-us-and-others-seek-influence</guid></item><item><title>蓬勃发展的加密货币交易所在“TradFi”推送中获得标准普尔官方数据</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/booming-crypto-exchange-gets-official-s-p-data-in-tradfi-push</link><description>几十年来，标准普尔全球公司的指数部门一直将全球最受关注的股票基准授权给受监管的金融界的坚定支持者。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKko44gQT9Sc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/booming-crypto-exchange-gets-official-s-p-data-in-tradfi-push</guid></item><item><title>美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 和商品期货交易委员会 (CFTC) 定义哪些数字资产是证券</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/sec-cftc-move-to-define-which-digital-assets-are-securities</link><description>美国证券交易委员会周二发布了期待已久的“代币分类法”，这是在明确哪些类型的数字资产被视为证券方面向前迈出的关键一步。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iHHzK3ubKnLg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 21:21:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/sec-cftc-move-to-define-which-digital-assets-are-securities</guid></item><item><title>无许可在去中心化金融中是双向的</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-17/permissionless-works-both-ways-in-decentralized-finance-defi</link><description>DeFi 出了岔子&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iZftIEA6rCys/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-17/permissionless-works-both-ways-in-decentralized-finance-defi</guid></item><item><title>埃里克·特朗普如何成为中国最大的加密货币公司之一的盟友</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-03-17/trump-s-son-and-a-mysterious-chinese-crypto-giant-are-in-business-together</link><description>&lt;p&gt;比特大陆多年来一直受到矿机安全问题的困扰。但这并没有阻止它与第一家庭的一位重要成员开展业务。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFuTRCtHymHY/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 20:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-03-17/trump-s-son-and-a-mysterious-chinese-crypto-giant-are-in-business-together</guid></item><item><title>伊朗战争震撼市场之际，比特币令人惊讶，成为平静的绿洲</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/bitcoin-surprises-as-oasis-of-calm-while-iran-war-jolts-markets</link><description>自与伊朗的战争爆发以来，加密货币已成为资产类别中的赢家，但数字资产的弹性可能只是时间问题。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iq.WbBpsI2Kk/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 06:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/bitcoin-surprises-as-oasis-of-calm-while-iran-war-jolts-markets</guid></item><item><title>万事达卡以高达 18 亿美元收购稳定币公司 BVNK</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/mastercard-to-buy-stablecoin-startup-bvnk-for-up-to-1-8-billion</link><description>万事达卡公司表示，将以高达 18 亿美元的价格收购稳定币基础设施初创公司 BVNK，四个月前，BVNK 与 Coinbase Global Inc. 就一项约 20 亿美元的交易进行的谈判破裂。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ittMqtxNQ0ro/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 12:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/mastercard-to-buy-stablecoin-startup-bvnk-for-up-to-1-8-billion</guid></item></channel></rss>